---
// /dashboard is superseded by /app — the real live dashboard (root index.html served at
// earn-defi.com/app). This page used to be a weaker Astro dashboard with stale/dead panels;
// it now redirects so there is ONE canonical dashboard. (_redirects also maps /dashboard→/app;
// this in-page redirect guarantees it even where the static page would otherwise be served.)
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0; url=/app" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="/app" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <title>Redirecting to dashboard — SPA</title>
  </head>
  <body style="background:#0b0c10;color:#e2e4ec;font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh;margin:0">
    <script is:inline>location.replace('/app');</script>
    <p>Redirecting to the live dashboard — <a href="/app" style="color:#1ed8a0">/app</a>…</p>
  </body>
</html>
